{"word":"Sheba","slug":"sheba","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sheba</b> <a href=\"#/H7614\">H7614</a><br/><a href=\"#/H7652\">H7652</a> <br/> 1. Son of Raamah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=7'>Gen 10:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=9'>1Ch 1:9</a><br/> 2. Son of Joktan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=10&verse=28'>Gen 10:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=22'>1Ch 1:22</a><br/> 3. Son of Jokshan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=3'>Gen 25:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=32'>1Ch 1:32</a><br/> 4. A Benjamite who led an insurrection against David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20'>2Sa 20</a><br/> 5. A Gadite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=13'>1Ch 5:13</a><br/> 6. A city of Simeon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=2'>Jos 19:2</a><br/> 7. Country of:<br/> - Queen of Sheba, visits Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=13'>1Ki 10:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=12'>2Ch 9:12</a> <br/> - Kings of, bring gifts to Solomon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=72&verse=10'>Psa 72:10</a> <br/> - Rich in gold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=72&verse=15'>Psa 72:15</a> <br/> - Rich in incense<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=20'>Jer 6:20</a> <br/> - Merchandise of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=23'>Eze 27:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=38&verse=13'>Eze 38:13</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning the people of, coming into the kingdom of Messiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=60&verse=6'>Isa 60:6</a><br/><a href='S:Sabeans'>Sabeans</a> "}]}